      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir ta nenoseedṣiga Afina deht/ ko wiꞥſch bij islehjts/ un Jerusalemi ar nenoseedṣigu Afina peepildiſe/ tapehz ne gribbeja tas KUNGS peedoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kaſ wehl no Jojakima Leetahm atleek/un wiſs/ko wiꞥſch irr darrijs/ tas irr rakſtihts to Kehniſu no Juhda Laiku-Grah-mata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jojakims aismigge ar faweem Tehweem/ un wiꞥſch Dehls Jojakins tappe par Keh-ninu wiꞥna Weeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Egiptes Kehniſch ne iſgahie kwairg no fawas Sem-mes/ jo tas Babeles Kehniſch bij no Egiptes Uppees lihds tai Uppei Wrat wiſu ussehmis/ kas tam Egiptes Kehnikam pee-derreja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jojakins btja afsonnavdef-mits Gaddus wezz/ kad tas par Kehniku tappe/ wa waldiia trihs Mehneschne Jerusaleme. Un wiꞥna Mahteſ btja Neista Wahrd/ Elnatana Meita no Jerusalemes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrija/ kas tam KUNGAM ne patikke/ ittin ka wiꞥna Tehws bij darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tanni Laika zehlehs Ne.bukad Nezara ta Babeles Kehnt-na Kalpi us Jerusalemi/ un nah-ze prett to Pilsfahtu apmesda-mces.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Nebukadnezars tas Babeles Kehniſch nahze pats prett to Pilsfahtu/ kad wiꞥna\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad iſgahje Jojakins Kehniſch no Juhda pee to beles Kehniſu ar fawu Malun faweem Kalpeem/ un fau Ahwerſteem un Kambar-Junreem/ un tas Babeles Kehniſachme to astota Gadda fan Waldifchanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch isneffe no renes wiſas Mantas ta KlSA Namma/ un wiſas Kelna Namma Mantas/ un fa te wiſsus Selta Trankus/Salaimans tas Israela niſsch eekſch ta KUNGA Noma bij darrijs/ un ka tas KUDbij runnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch afswedde wiſu Jerusalemi ar wiſſeem leem-Kungeem/ un ar wiſWarreneem desmits tuhkſtoſcZeetuma/ ir wiſsus Remmetchun Kallejus/ ne weens tappelizzinahts/ ka tee nabbagi Smes Laudis ween.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta afswedde wiꞥſch jakinu us Babeli/ lihds ar Kehnika Mahti/ un ta KehnSeewahm/ un wiꞥna KambarJunkureem. Un tahe SenWarreneem/ tohs afswe wiꞥſch no Jerusalemes us Bali Zeetuma.\n"
    },
